PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FA couple have been jailed for life
OL,7,Fafter murdering their 13-week-old baby.
OL,9,FKlevi, 37, and Nivalda Santos Pirjani,
OL,10,F34, "systematically abused" their son
OL,11,FMiguel, leaving him with numerous
OL,12,Fbroken bones and a bleed on the brain
OL,13,Fafter a "series of episodes of
OL,14,Fviolence".
OL,16,FThe pair, from Seacombe, on the
OL,17,FWirral, tried to blame each other for
OL,18,Ftheir son's death, but were
OL,19,Funanimously convicted of his murder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FJailing the couple for life, Mr
OL,7,FJustice Jay handed Klevi Pirjani, who
OL,8,Fwas said to have referred to Miguel as
OL,9,Fa "monster" and "it", a minimum term
OL,10,Fof 19 years, while his wife Nivalda
OL,11,Fwas given a minimum term of 15 years.
OL,13,F"Migel was 13-and-a-half weeks old
OL,14,Fwhen he died. You were his parents,
OL,15,Fand you killed him by what must have
OL,16,Fbeen an act of appalling violence,
OL,17,Fintending him to suffer really serious
OL,18,Fharm," the judge told them.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,F"It is possible that you intended to
OL,7,Fkill him to be rid of him, but I am
OL,8,Fnot sure that was your intention."
OL,10,FHe added: "I cannot say precisely when
OL,11,For how Miguel was fatally battered or
OL,12,Feven be sure about which of you
OL,13,Ffatally battered him. Only you two
OL,14,Fknow. You have chosen not to tell
OL,15,Fanyone.
OL,17,F"What exactly happened to Miguel that
OL,18,Fmorning remains the guilty secret of a
OL,19,Fwarped relationship where you came
OL,20,Ffirst to one another. The interest of
OL,21,FTeam Klevi Nivalda came first.
OL,26,@rD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,F"His death was a battered baby death
OL,7,Fat both of your hands. The jury were
OL,8,Fsure it was encouraged by the other of
OL,9,Fyou, both of you intending Miguel to
OL,10,Fsuffer at least grievous bodily harm.
OL,12,F"The fatal assault was not a one off
OL,13,Fincident that came out of the blue."
OL,15,FLiverpool Crown Court heard Merseyside
OL,16,FPolice was first called to the
OL,17,Fcouple's address on 24 November 2024
OL,18,Ffollowing a 999 call from Klevi
OL,19,FPirjani that his three-month-old son
OL,20,Fhad been found unresponsive at home.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FPeter Wright KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt during the trial: "He told the
OL,8,Foperator that Miguel just stopped
OL,9,Fbreathing.
OL,11,F"Curiously, he referred to his son as
OL,12,Fit. It just stopped breathing.
OL,14,F"It is a matter for you to consider in
OL,15,Fdue course as to whether this was a
OL,16,Fproduct of distress on his part, a
OL,17,Flanguage barrier or an unintended
OL,18,Findication of his attitude towards
OL,19,FMiguel."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FParamedics were able to recover a
OL,7,Fpulse and Miguel was admitted to Alder
OL,8,FHey Children's Hospital where medical
OL,9,Ftests confirmed he had a fractured
OL,10,Fskull and rib fractures. He also had
OL,11,Ffractures of varying ages, the court
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FMiguel was put on to life support, but
OL,15,Fdied five days later on 29 November.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FMr Wright added during the
OL,7,Fprosecution's opening: "At the time of
OL,8,Fhis passing, his mother was permitted
OL,9,Fto hold his hand. Whilst present, she
OL,10,Fwas heard to say 'I should have
OL,11,Fprotected you'."
OL,13,FA post mortem examination revealed
OL,14,Ffurther injuries, including retinal
OL,15,Fhaemorrhages, displaced skull bones,
OL,16,Fbleeding on both sides of the brain,
OL,17,Fbleeding around the cervical cord and
OL,18,Fa fatal hypoxic ischaemic brain injury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FUnder interview, Nivalda Pirjani gave
OL,7,Fa prepared statement to detectives in
OL,8,Fwhich she described Klevi as being
OL,9,Fabusive and violent.
OL,11,FShe said she did not blame her partner
OL,12,Ffor Miguel's injuries but said "she
OL,13,Fwas frightened of him and feared what
OL,14,Fhe may do".
OL,16,FShe also went on to repeat her claim
OL,17,Fthat her husband was the one
OL,18,Fresponsible for looking after Miguel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,FWhen he was questioned, Klevi Pirjani
OL,7,Fdisputed Nivalda's claims and said
OL,8,Fthat no concerns had been raised
OL,9,Fduring previous appointments with
OL,10,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,12,FHe also queried whether Miguel's rib
OL,13,Ffractures could have been caused by
OL,14,Fresuscitation efforts.
OL,16,FSenior Investigating officer Detective
OL,17,FInspector Holly Chance said: "I've
OL,18,Fbeen in the organisation 20 years and
OL,19,FI have never picked up a case like
OL,20,Fthis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,F"It's just so hard to comprehend and
OL,7,Funderstand how a parent can inflict
OL,8,Fsuch injuries on a 13-week-old baby.
OL,10,F"All that baby should have felt is
OL,11,Flove by the parents, the have the
OL,12,Fresponsibility to care for him but
OL,13,Finstead they've tortured him."
OL,15,FShe added: "Baby Miguel's life was
OL,16,Fcruelly cut short at the hands of his
OL,17,Fparents who were meant to nurture and
OL,18,Fprotect him from harm.
OL,26,@wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774365082
OL,3,CCouple who 'systematically abused' 13-
OL,4,Cweek-old son jailed for his murder
OL,6,F"We hope this sentencing provides some
OL,7,Fsense of justice for Miguel's wider
OL,8,Ffamily who won't be able to see him
OL,9,Fgrow up and our thoughts remain with
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"This was a tragic and extremely
OL,13,Fdistressing case for the investigation
OL,14,Fteam to work on, and I want to take
OL,15,Fthis opportunity to recognise their
OL,16,Fdetermination to seek justice for baby
OL,17,FMiguel, as well as the support
OL,18,Freceived from the Crown Prosecution
OL,19,FService."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
